title: Babymetal - Babymetal (2014) (Bonus DVD)
description:
This is an extremely limited Japanese release bonus DVD that came with Babymetal's 2014 Album.
DVD contains music videos for five singles, audio commentary from the members, live footage taken from SUMMER SONIC 2013, live footage performing new song's and more. *The DVD disc is encoded for region 2 (Japan, Europe, and Middle East), and no subtitles are included.

This is not my upload and I cannot find who originally uploaded it.I only found 1 place online that had it and being such a fan I did not have the money to bid 80 plus bucks for a copy of it on ebay.
So thank you again to original uploader.
